Detailed Description

cvmx_sso_bist_stat

SSO_BIST_STAT = SSO BIST Status Register

Contains the BIST status for the SSO memories ('0' = pass, '1' = fail). Note that PP BIST status is not reported here as it was in previous designs.

There may be more for DDR interface buffers. It's possible that a RAM will be used for SSO_PP_QOS_RND.
